constructor.details: Initializes the contract setting the address provided by the deployer for the PancakeSwap Router and Starlay Finance Protocol Lending Pool.

payDebt(address,uint256,address).details: Pays the debt of the user with the token provided by the user.

params._amount: The amount of token to be used to pay the debt.
params._onBehalfOf: The address of the user who wants to pay the debt.
params._token: The address of the token to be used to pay the debt.

swap(address,address,uint256,uint256).details: Swaps the tokenB for tokenA and transfers the tokenA to the user.

params._amountA: The amount of tokenA to be received by the user.
params._amountB: The amount of tokenB to be swapped for tokenA.
params._tokenA: The address of the token to be received by the user.
params._tokenB: The address of the token to be swapped for tokenA.

swapAndPayDebt(address,address,uint256,u.details: Swaps the tokenB for tokenA and transfers the tokenA to the user and pays the debt of the user with the token provided by the user.

params._amountA: The amount of tokenA to be received by the user.
params._amountB: The amount of tokenB to be swapped for tokenA.
params._onBehalfOf: The address of the user who wants to pay the debt.
params._tokenA: The address of the token to be received by the user.
params._tokenB: The address of the token to be swapped for tokenA.

documentation.text:
@dev Initializes the contract setting the address provided by the deployer for the
 PancakeSwap Router and Starlay Finance Protocol Lending Pool.

@dev Contract which provides the functionality to swap and pay debt
 for the user with debt on Starlay Finance Protocol with any supported tokens
 on ArthSwap which is a fork of PancakeSwap on Astar Network.
 The contract is deployed on Astar Network(0xaA5d4E34ba6D8079DCB6982Ef09b1175DE6b3414) and the user can swap and pay debt,
 currently the user can only pay his variable debt.
